    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099350/extras/5cf8a6d3973a35549f3a41c82d43d607.avif?t=1731478057\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099350/extras_big/5cf8a6d3973a35549f3a41c82d43d607.avif?t=1731478057 width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099350/extras/6ec01839171d4c377d4065593d0a333e.avif?t=1731478057\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099350/extras_big/6ec01839171d4c377d4065593d0a333e.avif?t=1731478057 width=800 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore 10+ unique levels from the treacherous Backrooms. Each level has different entities, objects, and phenomena associated with that level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099350/extras/b00073df4d214ec9f9241cbe067c3c64.avif?t=1731478057\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099350/extras_big/b00073df4d214ec9f9241cbe067c3c64.avif?t=1731478057 width=800 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend yourself from 20+ entities that are hunting you down. Each entity has different properties and inhabits different levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099350/extras/91422370e52fa8d20227cf1895028b74.avif?t=1731478057\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099350/extras_big/91422370e52fa8d20227cf1895028b74.avif?t=1731478057 width=800 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you adventure around, you will come across various items scattered across each level. Be careful though, as not all objects you find will help you. All items are different, and they all serve different purposes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099350/extras/60b3fe2509830ff7baa4441914b78f98.avif?t=1731478057\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099350/extras_big/60b3fe2509830ff7baa4441914b78f98.avif?t=1731478057 width=800 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While you are trying to find your way around the Backrooms, you may experience unexplainable phenomena. Anything can happen in this place, so come prepared, and no-clip into the Backrooms today.</p>",
